Copy link












                            Drop-In Spaces
                    

                Get the support you need, when and how you need it
            












                            Workshops
                    

                Learn about mental health topics and develop new coping skills
            












                            Peer Support
                    

                Connect with other UIC students and improve your mental health
            












                            Mind-Body Programs
                    

                Take a deeper dive into coping skills like mindfulness, self-compassion, and emotion regulation
            









